==Relation to other polynomials==

Affine q-Krawtchouk polynomials → [[Little q-Laguerre polynomials]]：

: <math>\lim_{a \to 1}=K_n^\text{aff}(q^{x-N};p,N\mid q)=p_n(q^x;p,q)</math>

